sinsider.com%2Fapple-dependent-on-china-economy-manufacturing-problem-2023-9%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%23%3A~%3Atext%3DDespite%2520recent%2520efforts%2520to%2520diversify%2Cfrom%2520China%2520(%252474%2520billion).%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Emore%20iPhones%20were%20sold%20in%20China%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20the%20US%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20still%20extracts%20cash%20out%20of%20China%20through%20Facebook%20and%20Instagram%20ads%20it%20sells%20to%20Chinese%20companies.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECFO%20Susan%20Li%20told%20investors%20in%20Meta's%20third-quarter%20earnings%20call%20that%20its%20gaming%20and%20commerce%20segments%20%26quot%3Bbenefited%20from%20strong%20spend%20among%20advertisers%20in%20China%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20their%20spending%20%26quot%3Baccelerated%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20company%20in%20the%20third%20quarter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment%2C%20made%20outside%20of%20normal%20working%20hours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-returns-china-striking-deal-tencent-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699617274000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654e0955b788914e5553c2fc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-returns-china-striking-deal-tencent-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Meta%20sells%20ads%20to%20Chinese%20companies%20but%20it%20isn't%20allowed%20to%20operate%20its%20platforms%20in%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jmann%40insider.com%20(Jyoti%20Mann)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-returns-china-striking-deal-tencent-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chandrayaan-3%20Top%20Scientist%20To%20Give%20Away%202%20Years'%20Salary%20To%20Alma%20Mater%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Chandrayaan-3%20mission%20brought%20out%20the%20best%20of%20the%20engineering%20skills%20of%20scientists%20from%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%2C%20and%20now%20their%20charitable%20deeds%20are%20making%20them%20new%20icons%20of%20philanthropy.%20Still%20in%20debt%20for%20his%20home%20loan%2C%20the%20hands-on%20leader%20for%20the%20success%20of%20the%20lander%20Vikram%20has%20donated%20more%20than%20two%20years%20of%20his%20take-home%20salary%20to%20his%20alma%20mater.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20P%20Veeramuthuvel%2C%2046%2C%20the%20son%20of%20a%20railway%20technician%2C%20is%20the%20project%20director%20of%20Chandrayaan-3%20and%20he%20successfully%20steered%20the%20historic%20soft-landing%20on%20the%20Moon's%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20that%20remarkable%20feat%2C%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20on%20Gandhi%20Jayanti%20awarded%20him%20and%20eight%20of%20his%20colleagues%20from%20the%20state%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20each%20as%20a%20gift.%20He%20has%20now%20decided%20to%20donate%20the%20entire%20amount%20to%20the%20alumni%20associations%20of%20the%20institutions%20he%20studied%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20scientist%2C%20Dr%20M%20Sankaran%2C%20the%20Director%20of%20the%20UR%20Rao%20Satellite%20Centre%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20has%20also%20decided%20to%20donate%20the%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20award%20money%20to%20the%20alumni%20associations%20of%20Thanthai%20Periyar%20Government%20Arts%20and%20Science%20College%2C%20Thiruchirapalli%20and%20the%20Raja%20Serforji%20Government%20Arts%20and%20Science%20College%2C%20Thanjavur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Veeramuthuvel%20says%20Chandrayaan's%20success%20was%20%26quot%3Bmore%20about%20we%20and%20less%20about%20me%26quot%3B%2C%20so%20the%20award%20had%20to%20be%20shared%20and%20the%20best%20option%20was%20to%20give%20to%20the%20institutions%20that%20shaped%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20conscience%20was%20not%20permitting%20me%20to%20take%20this%20large%20amount%20of%20award%20money%2C%20hence%20donation%20was%20the%20best%20option%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Veeramuthuvel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20first%20award%20money%20he%20has%20ever%20received%2C%20the%20rocket%20scientist%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Veeramuthuvel's%20take-home%20salary%20is%20about%20Rs%201%20lakh%20per%20month%20and%20he%20has%20donated%20more%20than%20two%20years%20of%20his%20would-be%20earnings%20to%20his%20alma%20maters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20come%20from%20a%20poor%20family%2C%20having%20studied%20in%20a%20government%20railway%20school%20in%20Villupuram%20and%20yet%20money%20does%20not%20mean%20much%20to%20me.%20ISRO%20gives%20us%20a%20rich%20environment%20to%20contribute%20towards%20national%20development%20and%20that%20is%20most%20satisfying%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Veeramuthuvel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20build%20his%20home%2C%20Dr%20Veeramuthuvel%20had%20taken%20a%20loan%20of%20Rs%2072%20lakh%20from%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%2C%20and%20he%20is%20still%20paying%20off%20that%20loan.%20Yet%2C%20he%20said%20the%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20windfall%20is%20not%20his%20to%20keep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Veeramuthuvel's%20wife%20Kavita%20Balasubramani%20is%20a%20homemaker%20and%20their%20daughter%20studies%20in%20a%20gurukulam%20in%20Coimbatore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Veeramuthuvel%20said%20he%20worked%20at%20least%2080%20every%20week%20and%20it%20went%20on%20continuously%20for%20four%20long%20years%20-%202019%20to%202023.%20His%20comment%20comes%20days%20after%20Infosys%20co-founder%20NR%20Narayana%20Murthy%20suggested%20young%20people%20should%20put%20in%2070%20works%20of%20work%20a%20week%2C%20which%20sparked%20a%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20Herculean%20task%20of%20a%20successful%20soft-landing%20on%20the%20Moon%20had%20to%20be%20achieved%20and%20all%20through%20these%20four%20years%2C%20I%20didn't%20take%20a%20single%20vacation%20or%20holiday%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Veeramuthuvel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandhya%20Venugopal%20Sharma%2C%20the%20additional%20secretary%20for%20the%20Department%20of%20Space%2C%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20said%20Dr%20Veeramuthuvel%20wants%20to%20equally%20share%20the%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20award%20to%20the%20alumni%20associations%20of%20Elumalai%20Polytechnic%20college%2C%20Villupuram%3B%20Sri%20Sairam%20Engineering%20College%2C%20West%20Tambaram%2C%20Chennai%3B%20National%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(NIT)%2C%20Tiruchirapalli%2C%20and%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(IIT)%20Madras%2C%20Chennai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeither%20the%20central%20government%20nor%20ISRO%20has%20announced%20any%20awards%20for%20the%20spectacular%20lunar%20achievement.%20Demands%20had%20been%20made%20that%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20core%20team%20of%20about%20150%20people%20be%20given%2010%20increments%20and%20all%20of%20ISRO%20be%20given%20a%20specially%20minted%20gold%20coin%2C%20but%20this%20is%20yet%20to%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20did%20pass%20a%20special%20resolution%20by%20the%20cabinet.%20The%20parliament%20also%20praised%20the%20space%20community%20for%20this%20gratifying%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699616820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F1a8acgrg_p-veeramuthuvel_625x300_10_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisro-chandrayaan-3-top-scientist-dr-p-veeramuthuvel-to-donate-2-year-worth-of-salary-to-alma-mater-4564331%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Chandrayaan-3%20mission%20brought%20out%20the%20best%20of%20the%20engineering%20skills%20of%20scientists%20from%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%2C%20and%20now%20their%20charitable%20deeds%20are%20making%20them%20new%20icons%20of%20philanthropy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news