%80%98Operation%20Chabutra%E2%80%99%20Is%20Turning%20Violent%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09165426%2FF9yZn8Ka0AEtKGZ.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20term%20that%20gained%20notoriety%20in%20Hyderabad%20recently%20is%20%E2%80%9Cchabutra.%E2%80%9D%20Contrary%20to%20the%20local%20population%E2%80%99s%20perception%20of%20a%20chabutra%20as%20a%20place%20of%20social%20gathering%2C%20it%20is%20perceived%20by%20the%20Hyderabad%20South%20Zone%20police%20as%20a%20place%20where%20youngsters%20indulge%20in%20illegal%20activities%20and%20criminal%20conspiracies%20late%20at%20night.%20This%20has%20led%20to%20a%20new%20form%20of%20policing%3A%20temporary%20detention%20of%20youngsters%20who%20step%20out%20after%20midnight%20in%20the%20city.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202015%2C%20Sri%20Satyanarayan%20the%20deputy%20commissioner%20(DCP)%20of%20the%20South%20Zone%20police%20initiated%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWLi-p0PRrBg%3Ffeature%3Dshared%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EOperation%20Romeo%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHXRu_RB307I%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EOperation%20Chabutra%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20discourage%20young%20individuals%20from%20gathering%20at%20chabutras%20and%20engaging%20in%20allegedly%20harmful%20activities.%20This%20practice%20was%20primarily%20aimed%20at%20raising%20awareness%20about%20the%20dangers%20of%20underage%20reckless%20bike%20riding%2C%20encouraging%20youngsters%20to%20use%20their%20time%20wisely%20and%20discouraging%20unnecessary%20late-night%20roaming%20that%20the%20police%20believed%20could%20potentially%20contribute%20to%20criminal%20activities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20is%20a%20chabutra%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChabutra%20is%20a%20colloquial%20term%20used%20in%20Hyderabad%20that%20refers%20to%20a%20raised%20platform%20or%20a%20pavement%20area%20typically%20found%20outside%20houses%20in%20residential%20areas.%20These%20structures%20often%20serve%20as%20community%20spaces%20for%20neighbours%20and%20residents%20to%20congregate%2C%20relax%2C%20or%20engage%20in%20conversations.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHistorically%2C%20chabutras%20have%20played%20an%20integral%20part%20in%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20design%2C%20and%20cultural%20fabric%20and%20in%20fostering%20a%20sense%20of%20community%20and%20social%20interaction.%20The%20concept%20of%20a%20chabutra%20draws%20its%20inspiration%20from%20the%20traditional%20village%20settings%20in%20India%20where%20community%20members%20and%20elders%20would%20gather%20beneath%20a%20grand%20tree%20to%20engage%20in%20conversations%20and%20deliberate%20on%20matters%20concerning%20families%20and%20society.%20In%20many%20Indian%20villages%2C%20this%20platform%20also%20served%20as%20the%20assembly%20ground%20for%20the%20local%20panchayat%20to%20conduct%20their%20meetings.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20common%20practice%20in%20India%20to%20have%20small%20indoor%20and%20outdoor%20platforms%20within%20neighbourhoods%20where%20people%20sit%20and%20converse.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20time%20this%20concept%20transformed.%20What%20was%20once%20a%20symbol%20of%20community%20bonding%20started%20to%20be%20associated%20with%20gatherings%20of%20youngsters%2C%20especially%20late%20in%20the%20night.%20These%20gatherings%20often%20involved%20socialising%2C%20chatting%2C%20and%20sometimes%20activities%20that%20raised%20concerns%2C%20including%20fights.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhy%20are%20chabutras%20targeted%20by%20the%20police%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20police%20have%20been%20focusing%20their%20attention%20on%20chabutras%20due%20to%20a%20series%20of%20incidents%20in%20which%20conflicts%20between%20two%20groups%20or%20even%20disputes%20among%20friends%20escalated%20to%20tragic%20outcomes%2C%20including%20loss%20of%20life.%20These%20unfortunate%20incidents%20have%20raised%20concerns%20within%20the%20police%20force%20about%20night-time%20gatherings%20in%20the%20old%20city%20areas.%20Information%20provided%20by%20local%20media%20and%20police%20informants%20suggests%20a%20correlation%20between%20these%20gatherings%20and%20the%20occurrence%20of%20violent%20incidents.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETherefore%2C%20the%20police%20say%20they%20are%20laying%20more%20emphasis%20on%20ensuring%20that%20young%20individuals%20do%20not%20congregate%20in%20localities%20post-midnight.%20This%20%E2%80%9Cproactive%20approach%E2%80%9D%2C%20they%20say%2C%20aims%20to%20prevent%20confrontations%20and%20altercations%2C%20reduce%20the%20likelihood%20of%20violence%20and%20ultimately%20preserve%20public%20safety.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20police%E2%80%99s%20assumption%20that%20these%20gatherings%20could%20potentially%20lead%20to%20conflicts%20or%20illicit%20activities%20raises%20important%20questions.%20Indeed%2C%20there%20are%20instances%20of%20such%20gatherings%20causing%20disturbances%20to%20residents%20and%20also%20serving%20as%20locations%20for%20criminal%20activities.%20It%E2%80%99s%20crucial%20to%20recognise%20that%20within%20neighbourhoods%2C%20there%20are%20designated%20spots%2C%20often%20in%20alleyways%20or%20side%20streets%2C%20frequented%20by%20known%20troublemakers%20or%20individuals%20with%20criminal%20backgrounds.%20However%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20distinguish%20between%20these%20specific%20individuals%20and%20the%20broader%20community.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECan%20young%20people%20be%20prohibited%20from%20gathering%20with%20friends%3F%20Is%20it%20justifiable%20to%20curtail%20their%20freedom%20of%20peaceful%20assembly%20based%20on%20a%20few%20reported%20instances%20of%20crime%20in%20the%20old%20city%3F%20Does%20the%20law%20permit%20the%20detention%20and%20harassment%20of%20youth%2C%20simply%20for%20sitting%20outside%20their%20residences%3F%20These%20are%20critical%20questions%20that%20warrant%20thoughtful%20examination%20and%20consideration.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20a%20positive%20aspect%20to%20chabutras%20that%20merits%20consideration.%20It%20has%20been%20observed%20that%20when%20residents%2C%20including%20youngsters%2C%20gather%20in%20their%20localities%2C%20it%20serves%20as%20a%20deterrent%20to%20crime%20and%20criminal%20activities.%20The%20presence%20of%20community%20members%20can%20discourage%20outsiders%20from%20attempting%20criminal%20acts%2C%20as%20they%20would%20be%20less%20likely%20to%20go%20unnoticed%20or%20unchallenged.%20This%20highlights%20the%20potential%20for%20chabutras%20to%20provide%20a%20space%20for%20social%20interaction%20%3Cem%3Eand%3C%2Fem%3E%20enhance%20security%20and%20cohesion%20in%20the%20neighbourhood.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETherefore%20a%20nuanced%20approach%20that%20addresses%20the%20concerns%20posed%20by%20gatherings%20that%20lead%20to%20disturbances%20and%20criminal%20behaviour%20while%20preserving%20the%20valuable%20role%20they%20can%20play%20in%20maintaining%20a%20safe%20and%20connected%20neighbourhood%20environment%20is%20necessary.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPolice%20harassment%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20underlying%20motivation%20behind%20police%20operations%20in%20specific%20localities%20is%20complex%20and%20often%20influenced%20by%20various%20societal%20factors%2C%20including%20caste%2C%20class%2C%20and%20religious%20biases.%20To%20comprehend%20this%20intention%2C%20one%20must%20acknowledge%20the%20existing%20societal%20biases%20which%20shape%20the%20attitudes%20of%20government%20agencies%2C%20particularly%20the%20police.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHistorically%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20tendency%20to%20stereotype%20certain%20communities%20and%20areas%2C%20which%20subsequently%20impacts%20the%20orientation%20of%20law%20enforcement%20personnel.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20Hyderabad%E2%80%99s%20old%20city%2C%20it%20has%20often%20been%20portrayed%20as%20an%20area%20with%20potential%20criminal%20elements%2C%20extremists%2C%20and%20terrorists.%20The%20Muslim%20community%20which%20resides%20there%20has%20frequently%20faced%20police%20harassment%2C%20before%20and%20after%20the%20formation%20of%20Telangana.%20Muslim%20youth%20have%20been%20disproportionately%20targeted%20and%20detained%20in%20alleged%20terrorism%20cases%2C%20subjecting%20them%20to%20years%20of%20harassment%2C%20particularly%20following%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20demolition.%20This%20biased%20perception%20is%20not%20accidental%3B%20rather%2C%20it%20is%20a%20deliberate%20part%20of%20the%20training%20and%20conditioning%20of%20law%20enforcement%20agencies.%20Muslims%20are%20often%20unfairly%20portrayed%20as%20radicalised%20and%20potential%20extremists%20or%20terrorists%2C%20contributing%20to%20a%20global%20narrative%20that%20emerged%20post-9%2F11%2C%20when%20international%20agencies%20began%20associating%20terrorism%20with%20the%20Muslim%20community.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20biases%20against%20Muslims%2C%20caste%20and%20class%20factors%20also%20influence%20the%20mindset%20of%20bureaucrats%20and%20law%20enforcement%20officers.%20There%20is%20a%20perception%20that%20individuals%20from%20backward%20communities%20with%20lower%20socioeconomic%20backgrounds%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20engage%20in%20criminal%20activities.%20This%20perception%20leads%20to%20the%20targeting%20of%20poor%20and%20vulnerable%20localities%20through%20measures%20such%20as%20cordon%20and%20search%20operations%20and%20%E2%80%98Mission%20Chabutra%E2%80%99.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EConversely%2C%20affluent%20and%20educated%20neighbourhoods%20often%20escape%20similar%20scrutiny.%20This%20imbalance%20in%20police%20operations%20reflects%20a%20broader%20societal%20bias%2C%20where%20individuals%20from%20disadvantaged%20backgrounds%20are%20disproportionately%20targeted%2C%20while%20those%20from%20privileged%20backgrounds%20enjoy%20relative%20impunity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOperation%20Chabutra%20has%20been%20portrayed%20in%20a%20positive%20light%20by%20the%20police%20with%20the%20help%20of%20local%20media.%20But%20of%20late%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20surge%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjUat6S25AzY%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Evideos%20showing%20police%20using%20violent%20force%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20youngsters%2C%20including%20instances%20of%20the%20police%20continuously%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FNewsMeter_In%2Fstatus%2F1715981167537930405%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehitting%20teenagers%20with%20%3Cem%3Elathis%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20This%20escalation%20of%20violence%20on%20a%20large%20scale%20across%20an%20entire%20community%20of%20people%20is%20a%20dangerous%20trend%20emerging%20out%20of%20Hyderabad.%20While%20the%20local%20population%20initially%20supported%20a%20non-violent%20way%20of%20policing%20youth%2C%20they%20are%20increasingly%20concerned%20about%20this%20escalation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20tragedy%20of%20this%20exercise%20is%20that%20instead%20of%20following%20the%20rule%20of%20law%2C%20the%20police%20have%20become%20the%20lawmakers%20in%20Hyderabad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ES.Q.%20Masood%20is%20a%20social%20activist%20from%20Hyderabad%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699612203000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09165426%2FF9yZn8Ka0AEtKGZ.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fin-hyderabad-policing-of-teens-under-operation-chabutra-is-turning-violent%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20police%20have%20long%20seen%20the%20chabutras%20in%20Old%