e%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E-%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20captiancy%20change%20saga%20remains%20one%20of%20the%20most%20controversial%20topics%20in%20Indian%20cricketing%20history.%20It%20still%20isn't%20known%20what%20exactly%20transpired%20behind%20the%20scenes%20before%20Virat%20Kohli's%20exit%20as%20captain%20from%20all%20three%20formats%20of%20the%20game.%20Rohit%20Sharma%20took%20over%20the%20baton%20from%20Kohli%20and%20has%20since%20done%20wonders%20in%20the%20role.%20However%2C%20former%20India%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sourav%20Ganguly%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F197-sourav-ganguly-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESourav%20Ganguly%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20revealed%20that%20Rohit%20wasn't%20keen%20on%20taking%20up%20the%20role.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGanguly%2C%20in%20a%20chat%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhoNJjyA4ycI%5C%22%3EKolkata%20TV%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20revealed%20that%20he%20had%20even%20given%20an%20ultimatum%20to%20Rohit%2C%20saying%20either%20he%20accepts%20captaincy%20himself%20or%20Ganguly%20would%20announce%20his%20name%20anyway.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRohit%20Sharma%20wasn't%20keen%20on%20captaincy.%20It%20had%20gone%20to%20a%20stage%20where%20'%3Cem%3Eaapko%20ha%20bolna%20hai%20nahi%20toh%20main%20kar%20dunga%3C%2Fem%3E'.%20It%20had%20gone%20to%20that%20stage.%20Because%20he%20is%20an%20outstanding%20captain.%20After%20Virat%20Kohli%20left%2C%20he%20was%20the%20best%20man%20to%20lead%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dada%20revealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20why%20Rohit%20wasn't%20keen%20on%20taking%20up%20India%20captaincy%2C%20the%20legendary%20cricketer%20said%20that%20although%20he%20isn't%20aware%20of%20the%20exact%20reason%2C%20it%20could%20be%20down%20to%20workload.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDon't%20kn