%20spotted%20her%20with%20another%20woman%20in%20the%20CCTV%20footage.%20That%20was%20the%20last%20time%20anyone%20saw%20her.%20Ms%20Down%20was%20officially%20reported%20missing%20on%20November%203%2C%202003.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20police%20investigation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20year%20after%20Charlene%20disappeared%2C%20information%20was%20passed%20to%20police%20that%20led%20to%20the%20launch%20of%20a%20murder%20inquiry.%20Police%20were%20%26quot%3Bhoping%20for%20the%20best%2C%20but%20fear%20the%20worst%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20men%20were%20charged%20in%20connection%20with%20Charlene's%20murder%20but%20a%20jury%20was%20unable%20to%20reach%20a%20verdict.%20A%20retrial%20later%20collapsed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELancashire%20Police%20faced%20criticism%20over%20its%20handling%20of%20the%20case%20following%20an%20investigation%20by%20the%20Independent%20Police%20Complaints%20Commission%2C%20the%20body%20subsequently%20replaced%20by%20the%20Independent%20Office%20for%20Police%20Conduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWas%20she%20sexually%20exploited%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20decade%20after%20investigating%20the%20case%2C%20the%20Lancashire%20Police%20said%20they%20believe%20Charlene%20Downes%20is%20one%20of%20a%20number%20of%20girls%20who%20were%20sexually%20exploited%20in%20Blackpool.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20their%20search%2C%20the%20police%20questioned%20more%20than%203%2C000%20people%20and%20became%20aware%20to%20the%20huge%20number%20of%20vulnerable%20girls%20-%20some%20as%20young%20as%2011%20-%20being%20targeted%20by%20male%20sex%20offenders%20in%20Blackpool.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20day%20of%20her%20disappearance%2C%20Ms%20Down's%20parents%20hosted%20a%20man%20later%20revealed%20to%20be%20a%20convicted%20paedophile.%20Their%20guest%20had%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20four%20counts%20of%20sexual%20abuse%20of%20ten-year-old%20children.%20The%20parents%20later%20said%20they%20were%20unaware%20of%20his%