4588%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BGive%20Me%202%20Days%20To%20Disclose...%26quot%3B%3A%20SL%20Selector%20On%20World%20Cup%20'Conspiracy'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChief%20Selector%20Pramodaya%20Wickramasinghe%20on%20Friday%20alleged%20that%20Sri%20Lanka's%20disastrous%20show%20at%20the%20ongoing%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20was%20a%20result%20%26quot%3Bof%20a%20conspiracy%20from%20outside%26quot%3B.%20The%20Sri%20Lankan%20cricket%20team%20returned%20home%20early%20Friday%20morning%20from%20India%20after%20their%20five-wicket%20loss%20in%20the%20last%20group%20stage%20match%20against%20New%20Zealand%20in%20Bengaluru.%20Pressed%20for%20reasons%20for%20the%20poor%20performance%2C%20Wickramasingha%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20World%20Cup-winning%201996%20team%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3Bgive%20me%20two%20days%20to%20disclose%20everything%20about%20it.%20This%20was%20the%20result%20of%20a%20conspiracy%20from%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20sad%2C%20I%20am%20taking%20responsibility%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20reporters%20at%20the%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESri%20Lanka%20recorded%20their%20worst%20World%20Cup%20performance%20since%201992%2C%20winning%20only%20two%20of%20their%20nine%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20champions%20were%20marred%20by%20a%20series%20of%20injuries%2C%20warranting%20replacements%20outside%20the%20original%20squad.%20That%20even%20led%20to%20a%20change%20of%20captaincy%20mid%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20disastrous%20show%20against%20India%2C%20where%20they%20were%20all%20out%20for%2056%2C%20triggered%20a%20backlash%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sports%20minister%20then%20fired%20the%20governing%20body%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%20Cricket%20(SLC)%20which%20was%20then%20reinstated%20by%20the%20court%20of%20appeal%2C%20thus%20further%20deepening%20the%20crisis%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20a%20joint%20government%20and%20opposition%20resolution%20in%20parliament%20demanded%20t