0the%20Bihar%20caste%20survey%20is%20a%20revolutionary%20document.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20public%20document%2C%20the%20first%20ever%20after%201931%2C%20allowing%20for%20people%20to%20stand%20up%20and%20be%20counted.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20go%20down%20to%20the%20wire%2C%20on%20what%20each%20of%20the%20numbers%20unveiled%20mean.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWho%20are%20the%20people%20referred%20to%20by%20percentages%20in%20the%20survey%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EToday%20we%20look%20at%20Rangrez%20(43%2C347%20people)%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Rangrez%20are%20a%20community%20of%20dyers%20who%20have%20been%20a%20cultural%20symbol%20in%20this%20country.%20They%20have%20their%20own%20unique%20past.%20One%20might%20even%20say%20that%20the%20community%20has%20been%20the%20flag%20bearer%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20Ganga-Jamuni%20culture.%20For%20them%2C%20everyone%20is%20equal%20and%20there%20is%20no%20difference%20based%20on%20caste%20or%20religion.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20dyed%20and%20stamped%20clothes%2C%20and%20inspired%20classical%20poet%20Amir%20Khusrau%20to%20mention%20it%20in%20his%20famous%20verses%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20have%20snatched%20away%20all%20trace%20of%20me%20with%20just%20one%20glance%E2%80%A6%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EMay%20my%20life%20be%20sacrificed%20for%20you%2C%20o%20my%20cloth-dyer%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20have%20dyed%20me%20in%20your%20colour%20with%20just%20one%20glance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20307px)%2085vw%2C%20307px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22307%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%20838w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-210x300.jpg%20210w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-715x1024.jpg%20715w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682410%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22440%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20those%20who%20believe%20in%20a%20secular%20India%2C%20this%20song%20of%20Amir%20Khusrau%20evokes%20a%20pleasant%20emotion.%20But%20the%20truth%20is%20that%20the%20mechanisation%20of%20the%20textile%20industry%20has%20snatched%20away%20the%20livelihood%20of%20the%20dyers.%20Culturally%2C%20the%20downfall%20of%20the%20caste%20began%20when%20Rangrezi%20came%20to%20be%20divided%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETurning%20a%20few%20pages%20in%20history%2C%20one%20can%20see%20the%20golden%20past%20of%20the%20dyers.%20Be%20it%20the%20areas%20of%20Awadh%20or%20the%20era%20of%20Delhi%20Sultanate%20when%20the%20influence%20of%20the%20dyers%20in%20the%20Meena%20Bazaar%20of%20the%20Red%20Fort%20was%20no%20less%20than%20that%20of%20any%20Mansabdar.%20Dyers%20also%20dominated%20the%20Rohilkhand%20region%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20Varanasi%20was%20no%20less%20than%20their%20home.%20The%20work%20of%20the%20dyers%20on%20Banarasi%20saris%20speaks%20volumes%20even%20today.%20The%20Rangrez%20community%20also%20inhabited%20parts%20of%20Bihar%20and%20West%20Bengal%20and%20some%20areas%20in%20Punjab.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20caste-based%20survey%20report%20released%20by%20the%20Bihar%20government%2C%20at%20present%20their%20population%20is%20only%2043%2C347.%20The%20community%20resides%20in%20districts%20like%20Bhagalpur%2C%20Patna%2C%20Nalanda%2C%20Buxar%2C%20etc.%20Since%20it%20is%20quite%20a%20small%20number%2C%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20comprehensive%20research%20to%20find%20out%20the%20reason%20behind%20their%20numbers.%20One%20needs%20to%20find%20out%20where%20the%20dyers%20have%20gone%20whose%20shops%20used%20to%20keep%20the%20market%20abuzz.%20Did%20they%20change%20their%20caste%20after%20changing%20professions%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERangrez%20are%20mainly%20Muslims.%20However%2C%20there%20are%20Hindu%20Rangrez%20as%20well%2C%20whose%20work%20is%20similar%20to%20that%20of%20Muslim%20Rangrez.%20The%20population%20of%20such%20Rangwa%20people%20is%20only%203%2C001%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20far%20as%20the%20social%20status%20of%20the%20Muslim%20Rangrez%20community%20is%20concerned%2C%20they%20are%20considered%20Sunni%20Muslims%20and%20while%20there%20is%20no%20stigma%20of%20untouchability%20owing%20to%20their%20occupation%2C%20certain%20Ashraf%20Muslims%20look%20down%20upon%20them%2C%20like%20the%20Julahas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20far%20as%20their%20political%20participation%20is%20concerned%2C%20the%20population%20of%20this%20caste%20in%20Bihar%20is%20only%200.0332%25%20of%20the%20total%20population%20and%20in%20the%20current%20democratic%20political%20situation%2C%20this%20number%20casts%20negligible%20influence.%20It%20would%20not%20be%20an%20exaggeration%20to%20say%20that%20this%20community%20or%20caste%20and%20its%20profession%2C%20which%20has%20been%20braving%20significant%20social%2C%20cultural%2C%20political%20and%20economic%20hardships%2C%20is%20on%20its%20last%20leg%20because%20a%20lot%20has%20changed%20in%20the%20world.%20Some%20people%20are%20still%20trying%20to%20keep%20their%20art%20alive.%20But%20when%20they%20are%20no%20longer%20able%20to%20earn%20their%20bread%2C%20how%20long%20will%20they%20survive%20on%20an%20empty%20stomach%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20Hindi%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%20Read%20the%20Hindi%20original%C2%A0%3Ca%2