ian%20group%20Islamic%20Jihad%20in%20Gaza%20released%20a%20video%20on%20Thursday%20showing%20an%20elderly%20woman%20and%20a%20young%20boy%20who%20were%20among%20around%20240%20hostages%20seized%20by%20militant%20gunmen%20who%20attacked%20Israel%20on%20Oct.%207.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhamas-ally-shares-video-of-elderly-hostage-to-be-released-if-demands-met-4563576%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhamas-ally-shares-video-of-elderly-hostage-to-be-released-if-demands-met-4563576%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhamas-ally-shares-video-of-elderly-hostage-to-be-released-if-demands-met-4563576%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Gaza%2C%20Prayers%2C%20Screams%20At%20Hospitals%20As%20Anaesthetics%2C%20Medicines%20Run%20Out%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20little%20girl%20was%20weeping%20in%20pain%20and%20screaming%20%26quot%3BMummy%2C%20Mummy%26quot%3B%20while%20the%20nurse%20stitched%20up%20her%20head%20wound%20without%20using%20any%20anaesthetic%2C%20because%20none%20was%20available%20at%20the%20time%20at%20Al%20Shifa%20Hospital%20in%20Gaza%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20moments%20nurse%20Abu%20Emad%20Hassanein%20could%20recall%20as%20he%20described%20the%20struggle%20to%20deal%20with%20an%20unprecedented%20influx%20of%20wounded%20people%20and%20a%20dearth%20of%20pain%20relief%20medication%20since%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza%20started%20a%20month%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20we%20give%20some%20of%20them%20sterile%20gauze%20(to%20bite%20on)%20to%20reduce%20the%20pain%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hassanein.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20know%20that%20the%20pain%20they%20feel%20is%20more%20than%20someone%20would%20imagine%2C%20beyond%20what%20someone%20their%20age%20would%20stand%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20children%20like%20the%20girl%20with%20the%20head%20wound.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArriving%20at%20Al%20Shifa%20to%20have%20the%20dressing%20changed%20and%20disinfectant%20applied%20to%20a%20wound%20on%20his%20back%20caused%20by%20an%20air%20strike%2C%20Nemer%20Abu%20Thair%2C%20a%20middle-aged%20man%2C%20said%20that%20he%20was%20given%20no%20pain%20relief%20when%20the%20wound%20was%20originally%20stitched%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20kept%20reciting%20the%20Koran%20until%20they%20finished%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20started%20on%20Oct.%207%20when%20Hamas%20gunmen%20burst%20through%20the%20Gaza%20Strip's%20border%20fence%20with%20southern%20Israel.%20Israel%20says%20Hamas%20killed%201%2C400%20people%20and%20abducted%20240%2C%20in%20the%20worst%20day%20of%20carnage%20in%20Israel's%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20responded%20with%20an%20air%2C%20sea%20and%20ground%20assault%20on%20the%20densely%20populated%2C%20Hamas-controlled%20enclave%2C%20which%20health%20officials%20in%20Gaza%20say%20has%20killed%20more%20than%2010%2C800%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohammad%20Abu%20Selmeyah%2C%20the%20director%20of%20Al%20Shifa%20Hospital%2C%20said%20that%20when%20very%20large%20numbers%20of%20injured%20people%20have%20been%20brought%20in%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20deal%20with%20them%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20without%20adequate%20pain%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20gave%20as%20an%20example%20the%20immediate%20aftermath%20of%20an%20explosion%20at%20the%20Al%20Ahli%20Arab%20Hospital%20on%20Oct.%2017%2C%20when%20he%20said%20some%20250%20injured%20people%20arrived%20at%20Al%20Shifa%2C%20which%20has%20only%2012%20operating%20theatres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20had%20waited%20to%20operate%20on%20them%20one%20by%20one%2C%20we%20would%20have%20lost%20many%20of%20the%20wounded%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Abu%20Selmeyah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20forced%20to%20operate%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20without%20anaesthesia%2C%20or%20using%20simple%20anaesthesia%20or%20weak%20pain%20killers%20to%20save%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProcedures%20that%20have%20been%20performed%20by%20staff%20at%20Al%20Shifa%20under%20such%20circumstances%20have%20included%20amputating%20limbs%20and%20fingers%2C%20stitching%20up%20serious%20wounds%2C%20and%20treating%20serious%20burns%2C%20said%20Abu%20Selmeyah%2C%20without%20elaborating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPAIN%20OR%20DEATH%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20painful%20for%20the%20medical%20team.%20It%20is%20not%20simple.%20It%20is%20either%20the%20patient%20suffers%20pain%20or%20loses%20his%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20said%20the%20blast%20at%20the%20Al%20Ahli%20Arab%20Hospital%20was%20caused%20by%20a%20failed%20rocket%20launch%20by%20the%20Palestinian%20Islamic%20Jihad%20group.%20Palestinian%20Islamic%20Jihad%20and%20Hamas%20blamed%20an%20Israeli%20air%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20ally%20the%20United%20States%20said%20its%20own%20intelligence%20assessment%20supported%20Israel's%20explanation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Nasser%20Hospital%20in%20Khan%20Younis%2C%20in%20the%20south%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20director%20Dr%20Mohammad%20Zaqout%20said%20there%20had%20been%20a%20period%20early%20on%20in%20the%20war%20when%20anaesthetic%20supplies%20ran%20out%20completely%2C%20until%20aid%20trucks%20were%20allowed%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20procedures%20were%20carried%20out%20without%20anaesthesia%2C%20including%20Caesarian%20sections%20on%20women%2C%20and%20we%20were%20also%20forced%20to%20operate%20on%20some%20burns%20that%20way%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Zaqout.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20staff%20did%20their%20best%20to%20alleviate%20patients'%20pain%20with%20other%2C%20weaker%20medications%2C%20but%20this%20was%20inadequate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20the%20ideal%20solution%20for%20a%20patient%20inside%20an%20operating%20theatre%2C%20who%20we%20want%20to%20operate%20on%20with%20full%20anaesthesia%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%2012%20days%20of%20the%20war%2C%20no%20aid%20was%20allowed%20into%20Gaza.%20On%20Oct.%2021%2C%20a%20first%20convoy%20of%20aid%20trucks%20came%20in%20through%20the%20Rafah%20Crossing%20on%20the%20strip's%20border%20with%20Egypt.%20Since%20then%2C%20several%20convoys%20have%20entered%2C%20but%20the%20United%20Nations%20and%20international%20aid%20groups%20say%20the%20aid%20provided%20is%20nowhere%20near%20the%20scale%20needed%20to%20mitigate%20a%20humanitarian%20catastrophe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZaqout%20added%20that%20while%20the%20shortage%20of%20anaesthesia%20had%20been%20eased%20at%20his%20own%20hospital%20thanks%20to%20aid%20deliveries%2C%20there%20were%20still%20severe%20shortages%20at%20Al%20Shifa%20and%20at%20the%20Indonesian%20Hospital%2C%20both%20of%20which%20are%20in%20the%20heavily%20bombarded%20north%20of%20the%20strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699604640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fdlhhdu6o_gaza-_625x300_10_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-gaza-hamas-palestine-in-gaza-prayers-screams-at-hospitals-as-anaesthetics-medicines-run-out-4563363%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20little%20girl%20was%20weeping%20in%20pain%20and%20screaming%20%26quot%3BMummy%2C%20Mummy%26quot%3B%20while%20the%20nurse%20stitched%20up%20her%20head%20wound%20without%20using%20any%20anaesthetic%2C%20because%20none%20was%20available%20at%20the%20time%20at%20Al%20Shifa%20Hospital%20in%20Gaza%20City.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A