ndise%20can%20not%20have%20photographs%20or%20symbols%20of%20any%20political%20party%20or%20leader.%20Upon%20receiving%20a%20complaint%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20ordered%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Chemicals%20and%20Fertilizers%20to%20remove%20PM's%20photo%20from%20the%20sacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20no%20end%20to%20the%20shortage%20in%20sight%20and%20fearing%20delay%20in%20Rabi%20sowing%20season%2C%20anxious%20farmers%20are%20buying%20bags%20of%20fertiliser%20at%20over-inflated%20prices.%20Hari%20Singh%20Saini%2C%20a%20farmer%20from%20Entkhedi%20village%20near%20Bhopal%2C%20has%20managed%20to%20purchase%20only%2015%20bags%20of%20DAP%2C%20a%20phosphate-based%20fertiliser%2C%20for%20his%2012-acre%20land.%20%26quot%3BOur%20expenses%20have%20gone%20up%20by%2020%25.%20It%20has%20become%20very%20difficult.%20We%20will%20end%20up%20with%20a%20lower%20yield%2C%20earning%20close%20to%20nothing%20from%20this%20crop%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bhopal's%20Nipaniya%20Jat%20village%2C%20one%20farmer%20is%20being%20given%20one%20sack%20of%20DAP%20and%20two%20sacks%20of%20Urea.%20Even%20though%20fertiliser%20with%20the%20revised%20packaging%20is%20available%2C%20farmers%20complain%20of%20rising%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELokendra%20Jat%2C%20a%20local%20farmer%20says%20a%20bag%20of%20urea%20which%20used%20to%20be%2050%20kg%20bag%20is%20now%20repackaged%20into%2045%20kg%20bags%20while%20the%20price%20remains%20the%20same.%20%26quot%3BA%20bag%20of%20DAP%20used%20to%20cost%20Rs%201%2C200%20but%20its%20now%20Rs%201%2C365.%20The%20price%20of%20granular%20fertiliser%20has%20also%20gone%20up%20from%20Rs%20310%20to%20Rs%20468.%20This%20will%20impact%20the%20yield%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20Rewa%20and%20Dewas%20are%20not%20facing%20a%20shortage%20due%20to%20incorrect%20packaging%2C%20farmers%20complain%20of%20waiting%20in%20queues%20for%20over%20five%20hours%20and%20forced%20to%20make%20two%20to%20three%20trips%20to%20get%20fertiliser%20just%20a%20few%20bags%20of%20fertiliser.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20Mandsaur%2C%20the%20revision%20of%20packaging%20has%20led%20to%20a%20confusion%20with%20even%20the%20correctly%20packaged%20fertiliser%20being%20distributed%20at%20slow%20rates.%20Ramesh%20Masare%2C%20a%20local%20Tehsildar%20told%20NDTV%2C%20that%20the%20long%20queues%20are%20caused%20by%20farmers%20from%20other%20districts%20coming%20there%20to%20buy%20fertiliser%20but%20denied%20any%20news%20of%20shortage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20both%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20intensify%20their%20poll%20campaigns%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20issue%20also%20came%20up%20in%20the%20speeches%20of%20party%20leaders%20and%20Union%20ministers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20claimed%20that%20there%20is%20no%20fertiliser%20shortage%20in%20the%20state%20and%20denied%20any%20long%20queues%20outside%20distribution%20centres.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20BJP%20government%20is%20in%20power%2C%20there%20has%20never%20been%20any%20shortage%20of%20urea%20or%20fertiliser%20for%20the%20farmers.%20Delivery%20has%20been%20done%20on%20time%20to%20farmers%20without%20standing%20in%20queue.%20Even%20today%2C%20there%20is%20no%20problem%20in%20fertiliser%20distribution%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20while%20addressing%20a%20rally%20in%20MP%20accused%20BJP%20of%20%26quot%3Bcheating%20farmers%20and%20not%20doing%20anything%20for%20them%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20officials%20about%206.42%20lakh%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20urea%20arrived%20in%20the%20state%2C%202.86%20lakh%20metric%20tonnes%20has%20been%20sold%20with%203.56%20lakh%20metric%20tonnes%20leftover.%20Out%20of%20the%20total%204.31%20lakh%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20DAP%2C%202.03%20lakh%20metric%20tonnes%20has%20been%20distributed.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699601760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fikdm59n_madhya-pradesh-fertiliser_625x300_10_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffertiliser-shortage-in-madhya-pradesh-despite-abundant-stock-heres-why-4563396%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Farmers%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20are%20forced%20to%20wait%20in%20long%20queues%20to%20buy%20fertiliser%20after%20a%20full%20stock%20became%20unfit%20for%20sale%20due%20to%20negligence%20of%20officials.%20Weeks%20after%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20was%20imposed%2C%20officials%20failed%20to%20erase%20PM's%20face%20on%20packets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffertiliser-shortage-in-madhya-pradesh-despite-abundant-stock-heres-why-4563396%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffertiliser-shortage-in-madhya-pradesh-despite-abundant-stock-heres-why-4563396%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffertiliser-shortage-in-madhya-pradesh-despite-abundant-stock-heres-why-4563396%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22THDCIL%20inks%20pacts%20to%20develop%203%2C270%20MW%20renewable%20energy%20projects%20in%20K'taka%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699601608000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-08%2F13%2Ffull%2F1660380513-3128.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fthdcil-inks-pacts-to-develop-3-270-mw-renewable-energy-projects-in-k-taka-123111000363_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22THDCIL%20has%20a%20portfolio%20of%2010%20projects%20(hydro%2C%20thermal%2C%20wind%20%26amp%3B%20solar)%20with%20a%20total%20capacity%20of%204%2C516%20MW%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fthdcil-inks-pacts-to-develop-3-270-mw-renewable-energy-projects-in-k-taka-123111000363_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Exposure%20to%20Air%20Pollution%20Changes%20the%20Way%20Our%20Airways%20Behave%E2%80%99%3A%20Surge%20in%20Respiratory%20Symptoms%20in%20Delhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07121500%2Fimage-1480.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20national%20capital%E2%80%99s%20air%20quality%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fstory%2Fdelhi-ncr-pollution-air-quality-index-severe-artificial-rain-2460675-2023-11-09%5C%22%3Ehas%20reached%3C%2Fa%3E%20alarming%20levels%2C%20with%20adverse%20consequences%20not%20only%20on%20public%20health%20but%20also%20on%20the%20economic%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%E2%80%99s%20environment%20minister%20Gopal%20Rai%20on%20November%208%20held%20a%20meeting%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fstory%2Fdelhi-pollution-minister-gopal-rai-meets-iit-kanpur-team-to-discuss-possibility-of-artificial-rain-2460546-2023-11-08%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3Ea%20team%20from%20IIT%20Kanpur%20to%20discuss%20the%20possibility%20of%20artificial%20rainfall%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethrough%20cloud%20seeding%20to%20bring%20down%20the%20AQI%20(air%20quality%20index)%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20decided%20that%20artificial%20rain%20could%20be%20used%20in%20Delhi%20on%20November%2020-21%20if%20the%20weather%20is%20cloudy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pollution%20crisis%20in%20Delhi%20is%20primarily%20attributed%20to%20vehicular%20emissions%2C%20industrial%20activities%2C%20and%20crop%20burning%20in%20neighboring%20states.%20The%20concentration%20of%20harmful%20pollutants%20such%20as%20PM2.5%20and%20PM10%20particles%20has%20surged%2C%20leading%20to%20respiratory%20issues%2C%20cardiovascular%20problems%2C%20and%20a%20general%20decline%20in%20the%20overall%20well-being%20of%20the%20populace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIntense%20air%20pollution%20exposure%20is%20changing%20the%20way%20our%20airways%20behave%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20healthy%20people%20have%20also%20complained%20of%20the%20new%20onset%20symptom%20of%20cough%2C%20breathlessness%2C%20chest%20tightness%2C%20fatigue%2C%20headache%2C%20eye%20irritation%2C%20and%20sneezing.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20something%20new.%20This%20is%20what%20we%20see%20during%20this%20season.%20We%20have%20been%20seeing%20it%20for%20the%20last%20many%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr.%20Karan%20Madan%2C%20additional%20professor%2C%20Department%20of%20Pulmonary%2C%20Critical%20Care%20and%20Sleep%20Medicine%2C%20All%20India%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20(AIIMS)%2C%20told%3Cem%3E%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20way%20we%20see%20these%20symptoms%20when%20air%20quality%20goes%20down%20does%20tend%20to%20point%20out%20that%20these%20symptoms%20are%20related%20to%20worsening%20air%20pollution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20when%20asked%20if%20we%20can%20attribute%20these%20symptoms%20to%20a%20decline%20in%20air%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHealthy%20people%20get%20cough%2C%20hacking%20cough%2C%20allergies.%20We%20treat%20them%20just%20the%20way%20we%20treat%20asthma.%20Asthma%20is%20an%20allergic%20condition.%20Those%20healthy%20people%20who%20develop%20these%20symptoms%2C%20and%20are%20responding%20to%20inhaled%20steroids%2C%20it%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20incorrect%20to%20say%20that%20%5Bair%20pollution%5D%20is%20triggering%20asthma-like%20conditions%20or%20probably%20allergic%20conditions%20in%20healthy%20people.%20Many%20times%20their%20hacking%20cough%20also%20requires%20some%20treatments%20with%20steroids.%20It%20does%20mean%20that%20this%20intense%20air%20pollution%20exposure%20makes%20some%20changes%20in%20the%20way%20our%20airways%20behave%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20nature%20of%20respiratory%20illnesses%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20consistently%20noticing%20for%20the%20last%20many%20years%20that%20when%20viral%20infection%20is%20going%20on%2C%20we%20know%20that.%20But%20during%20these%20episodes%2C%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20find%20any%20viral%2C%20which%20is%20cause%20of%20the%20exacerbation.%20When%20the%20air%20quality%20goes%20down%2C%20many%20people%20start%20complaining%20of%20these%20acute%20respiratory%20symptoms.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20heart%20patients%2C%20it%20may%20be%20more%20harmful.%20There%20are%20studies%20to%20show%20that%20air%20pollution%20increases%20the%20risk%20of%20BP%3B%20hypertension%20increases.%20An%20increase%20in%20BP%20is%20not%20good%20for%20any%20heart%20patient.%20Data%20says%20very%20poor%20air%20quality%20is%20not%20good%20for%20patients%20with%20cardiac%20disease%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20a%20substantial%20number%20of%20patients%20with%20airway%20diseases%2C%20such%20as%20asthma%20and%20chronic%20obstructive%20pulmonary%20disease%20(COPD)%2C%20who%20are%20under%20the%20hospital%20follow-up%2C%20have%20reported%20a%20notable%20deterioration%20in%20their%20symptoms.%20Complaints%20include%20increased%20wheeziness%2C%20heightened%20breathlessness%2C%20and%20a%20greater%20need%20for%20inhalers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20severity%20has%20escalated%20to%20acute%20asthma%20attacks%2C%20leading%20to%20hospitalizations%20and%20necessitating%20intensified%20treatments%2C%20including%20the%20administration%20of%20oral%20steroids.%20The%20overall%20frequency%20of%20asthma%20exacerbations%20or%20attacks%20has%20shown%20a%20notable%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20have%20had%20acute%20asthma%20attacks%2C%20some%20of%20which%20required%20hospitalisations%2C%20and%20some%20have%20required%20escalation%20of%20their%20treatments.%20We%20had%20to%20give%20them%20oral%20steroids.%20Asthma%20exacerbation%20or%20attacks%20have%20increased%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20AIIMS%20director%20and%20senior%20pulmonologist%20Dr.%20Randeep%20Guleria%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fsevere-plus-air-leading-to-more-breathing-problems-ex-aiims-director-explains-101699270128237.html%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20news%20agency%20ANI%20that%20people%20with%20no%20respiratory%20diseases%20are%20also%20facing%20breathing%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRespiratory%20problems%20may%20increase%20in%20people%20with%20diseases%20like%20bronchitis%20or%20heart%20problems%2C%20resulting%20in%20decreased%20oxygen%20saturation%20and%20increased%20emergency%20visits.%20In%20OPD%20too%2C%20more%20patients%20with%20a%20complaint%20of%20breathing%20are%20coming.%20Hospitalisation%2C%20ICU%20admissions%2C%20and%20OPD%20referrals%20are%20increasing%20in%20patients%20and%20also%20in%20those%20people%20who%20are%20normal%20and%20have%20no%20disease%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr.%20Guleria%20told%20the%20news%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fdelhi-air-pollution-working-class-stays-outdoors-despite-health-issues-sees-a-cut-in-pay%5C%22%3EDelhi%20Air%20Pollution%3A%20Working%20Class%20Stays%20Outdoors%20Despite%20Health%20Issues%2C%20Sees%20a%20Cut%20in%20Pay%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EImpact%20on%20the%20economy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20pollution%20is%20the%20second%20biggest%20factor%20affecting%20human%20health%20in%20India%2C%20according%20to%20the%20World%20Air%20Quality%20Report%202022%2C%20prepared%20by%20Swiss%20organisation%20IQAir.%20The%20report%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fair-pollution-health-risk-india-annual-economic-cost-over-usd-150-billion-1928843-2022-03-24%5C%22%3Ewas%20released%3C%2Fa%3E%20globally%20in%20March%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%2C%20the%20problem%20of%20air%20pollution%20costs%20the%20Indian%20economy%20%2495%20billion%20per%20year.%20Therefore%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20need%20to%20reduce%20air%20pollution%20to%20increase%20economic%20growth.%3Cb%3E%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20found%20that%20if%20India%20had%20achieved%20safe%20air%20quality%20levels%20in%202019%2C%20its%20GDP%20would%20have%20increased%20by%20%2495%20billion%2C%20or%203%25%2C%20as%20Indian%20businesses%20would%20face%20lower%20costs%20and%20higher%20revenues.%20This%20means%20there%20was%20potential%20to%20return%20a%20value%20equal%20to%2050%25%20of%20all%20tax%20collected%20annually%2C%20or%20150%25%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20healthcare%20budget.%20Bringing%20clean%20air%20to%20India%20benefits%20the%20economy%20and%20businesses%20through%20lower%20absenteeism%2C%20higher%20on-the-job%20productivity%2C%20higher%20consumer%20footfall%20and%20lower%20premature%20mortality%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weforum.org%2Fagenda%2F2021%2F06%2Fair-pollution-india-economy-business%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20June%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699601400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07121500%2Fimage-1480.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fexposure-to-air-pollution-changes-the-way-our-airways-behave-surge-in-respiratory-symptoms-in-delhi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Apart%20from%20the%20detrimental%20health%20impact%2C%20the%20economic%20toll%20of%20air%20pollution%20on%20India%20is%20staggering.%20The%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20estimates%20an%20annual%20cost%20of%20%2495%20billion%2C%20or%203%25%20of%20India's%20GDP.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenv