ad%20there's%20fear%20and%20hate%20among%20people%20%E2%80%94%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsocial-media-dead-instagram-tiktok-bereal-replaced-group-chats-messaging-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esameness%20on%20social%20platforms%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20felt%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EK-Brooks%20didn't%20explicitly%20disclose%20the%20reason%20the%20site%20shut%20down.%20(Omegle%20did%20just%20settle%20a%20lawsuit%20that%20contained%20some%20horrible%20allegations%20of%20child%20abuse.)%20But%20he%20did%20allude%20to%20%26quot%3Battacks%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20platform%20that%20he%20said%20he%20no%20longer%20cared%20to%20fight%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3EAs%20much%20as%20I%20wish%20circumstances%20were%20different%2C%20the%20stress%20and%20expense%20of%20this%20fight%20%E2%80%94%20coupled%20with%20the%20existing%20stress%20and%20expense%20of%20operating%20Omegle%2C%20and%20fighting%20its%20misuse%20%E2%80%94%20are%20simply%20too%20much.%20Operating%20Omegle%20is%20no%20longer%20sustainable%2C%20financially%20nor%20psychologically.%20Frankly%2C%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20have%20a%20heart%20attack%20in%20my%2030s.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bigger%20context%20here%20is%20that%20Omegle%20had%20a%20serious%20issue%20with%20sexual%20content%20and%20minors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%202021%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Ftechnology-56085499%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EBBC%20report%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20problems%20it%20found%20on%20Omegle%20was%20alarming.%20The%20headline%3A%20%26quot%3BOmegle%3A%20Children%20expose%20themselves%20on%20video%20chat%20site.%26quot%3B%20And%20an%20organization%20that%20monitors%20online%20safety%20had%2077%2C000%20reports%20in%202020%20of%20%26quot%3Bself-generated%26quot%3B%20child%20sex%20abuse%20materials%20coming%20from%20the%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Omegle%20settled%20the%20lawsuit%2C%20the%20AP%20reported.%20It%20had%20been%20filed%20in%20Oregon%20in%202021.%20In%20the%20civil%20suit%2C%20a%20woman%20claimed%20she%20had%20been%20exploited%20and%20blackmailed%20into%20producing%20explicit%20material%20%E2%80%94%20starting%20when%20she%20was%20just%2011%20%E2%80%94%20by%20a%20man%20in%20his%20late%2030s%20who%20she%20met%20on%20Omegle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FRIPomegle%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23RIPomegle%3C%2Fa%3E%20%F0%9F%AA%A6%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThank%20you%20to%20our%20client%20A.M.%20for%20convincing%20Omegle%20of%20its%20human%20cost.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FnDWU4EZ6K1%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FnDWU4EZ6K1%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Carrie%20Goldberg%20(%40cagoldberglaw)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcagoldberglaw%2Fstatus%2F1722589547869946142%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%209%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2022%2F7%2F14%2F23216386%2Fomegle-lawsuit-section-230-district-ruling%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOmegle%20had%20tried%20to%20claim%20protection%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-section-230-internet-law-communications-decency-act-explained-2020-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESection%20230%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20federal%20law%20that%20basically%20says%20that%20platforms%20aren't%20responsible%20for%20their%20users'%20posts%20(with%20some%20caveats).%20The%20judge%20ruled%20against%20it%2C%20on%20grounds%20that%20its%20product%20was%20defective%20by%20design.%20%26quot%3BOmegle%20could%20have%20satisfied%20its%20alleged%20obligation%20to%20Plaintiff%20by%20designing%20its%20product%20differently%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0for%20example%2C%20by%20designing%20a%20product%20so%20that%20it%20did%20not%20match%20minors%20and%20adults%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20K-Brooks'%20message%20said%2C%20all%20platforms%20are%20susceptible%20to%20bad%20actors%20%E2%80%94%20and%20child%20predators%20certainly%20exist%20on%20other%20social%20sites%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20combination%20of%20Omegle's%20apparent%20appeal%20to%20teens%20and%20children%2C%20its%20anonymity%2C%20its%20ability%20to%20connect%20children%20to%20random%20adults%20in%20private%20conversations%2C%20and%20its%20tolerance%20of%20nudity%20all%20set%20it%20apart%20from%20many%20other%20social%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20a%20platform%20that%20seemed%20almost%20perfectly%20designed%20to%20allow%20some%20adults%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20its%20product%20flaws%20to%20target%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOmegle%20said%20on%20its%20front%20page%20that%20you%20had%20to%20be%20%26quot%3B18%2B%20or%2013%2B%20with%20parental%20permission%26quot%3B%20to%20use%20it.%20(By%20late%202022%2C%20the%20requirement%20stated%20%26quot%3B18%2B%20only.%26quot%3B)%20But%20it%20didn't%20require%20any%20actual%20age%20verification%2C%20so%20there%20was%20no%20way%20of%20blocking%20underage%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20site%20wasn't%20completely%20unmoderated%2C%20and%20it%20was%20not%20unaware%20of%20the%20possible%20dangers%20to%20children.%20According%20to%20K-Brooks's%20post%2C%20Omegle%20had%20worked%20with%20law%20enforcement%20and%20%26quot%3Bthere%20was%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20moderation%20behind%20the%20scenes%2C%20including%20state-of-the-art%20AI%20operating%20in%20concert%20with%20a%20wonderful%20team%20of%20human%20moderators.%20Omegle%20punched%20above%20its%20weight%20in%20content%20moderation%2C%20and%20I'm%20proud%20of%20what%20we%20accomplished%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20his%20statement%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20K-Brooks's%20note%20stood%20out%20from%20other%20announcements%20of%20a%20website%20or%20service%20shutting%20down.%20It%20was%20highly%20personal.%20He%20disclosed%20that%20he%20was%20a%20victim%20of%20child%20rape%20himself%20%E2%80%94%20and%20he%20was%20thoughtful%20about%20the%20current%20state%20of%20internet%20culture.%20(K-Brooks%2C%20who%20founded%20a%20new%20company%20called%20OctaneAI%2C%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20message%20on%20LinkedIn.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20his%20post%20also%20showed%20a%20very%20early%20internet%20attitude%20about%20trust%20and%20safety%20and%20content%20moderation%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0that%20bad%20actors%20will%20always%20exist%2C%20and%20there's%20just%20nothing%20you%20can%20do%20about%20them.%20That%20the%20platform%20is%20totally%20neutral%20and%20that%20it's%20not%20the%20platform's%20fault%20if%20bad%20things%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20clear%20reference%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupreme-court-decision-section-230-win-big-tech-trump-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESection%20230%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20post%3A%20%26quot%3BVirtually%20every%20tool%20can%20be%20used%20for%20good%20or%20for%20evil%2C%20and%20that%20is%20especially%20true%20of%20communication%20tools%2C%20due%20to%20their%20innate%20flexibility.%20The%20telephone%20can%20be%20used%20to%20wish%20your%20grandmother%20'happy%20birthday'%2C%20but%20it%20can%20also%20be%20used%20to%20call%20in%20a%20bomb%20threat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOmegle%20was%20a%20communication%20tool%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20it%20was%20used%20for%20harm%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit%20and%20multiple%20reports%20from%20the%20BBC%20and%20elsewhere.%20But%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fobama-section-230-tech-firms-regulated-treated-as-publishers-2020-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESection%20230%20doesn't%20offer%20a%20blanket%20protection%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20any%20website%20for%20anything%20bad%20that%20happens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20farewell%20message%2C%20K-Brooks%20wrote%20some%20poignant%20things%20about%20the%20state%20of%20the%20internet%2C%20and%20how%20it's%20changed%20since%20he%20founded%20the%20site%2014%20years%20ago.%20He%20described%20how%20as%20a%20young%20person%2C%20he%20longed%20for%20safe%20connection%20with%20strangers%2C%20and%20said%20the%20serendipity%20of%20those%20fun%20moments%20was%20magical.%20He%20also%20said%20he%20is%20worried%20about%20the%20future%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3EI%20worry%20that%2C%20unless%20the%20tide%20turns%20soon%2C%20the%20Internet%20I%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20may%20cease%20to%20exist%2C%20and%20in%20its%20place%2C%20we%20will%20have%20something%20closer%20to%20a%20souped-up%20version%20of%20TV%20%E2%80%94%20focused%20largely%20on%20passive%20consumption%2C%20with%20much%20less%20opportunity%20for%20active%20participation%20and%20genuine%20human%20connection.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20general%2C%20I%20agree.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-nostalgia-social-media-facebook-twitter-dead-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%2C%20too%2C%20mourn%20the%20loss%20of%20the%20joy%20and%20whimsy%20of%20the%20early%20internet%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20excitement%20of%20early%20social%20networks%2C%20and%20bemoan%20the%20current%20state%20of%20bland%20sameness%20%E2%80%94%20every%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkylie-jenner-kim-kardashian-instagram-stop-trying-to-be-tiktok-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplatform%20racing%20to%20be%20just%20like%20Tiktok%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20Omegle%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20not%20see%20that%20the%20negatives%20simply%20outweighed%20the%20positives.%20There%20was%20so%20much%20apparent%20danger%20to%20children%20for%20so%20long%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20seems%20that%20danger%20went%20unchecked%20without%20any%20truly%20meaningful%20changes%20to%20the%20site%20that%20would%20have%20prevented%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20sites%20from%20Web%202.0%20that%20I'll%20miss%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0Flickr%2C%20LiveJournal%2C%20old%20Twitter%2C%20Geocities%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-happened-to-tumblr-history-2014-girl-gen-z-millennials-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeven%20Tumblr's%20heyday%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20Omegle%20isn't%20one%20to%20be%20sad%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fomegle-is-dead-section-230-csam-allegations-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699578421000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654d5f16b788914e5553ac3f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fomegle-is-dead-section-230-csam-allegations-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20anonymous%20chat%20site%20could%20be%20fun%2C%20but%20it%20never%20solved%20its%20problem%20of%20potentially%20endangering%20children.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22knotopoulos%40gmail.com%20(Katie%20Notopoulos)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fomegle-is-dead-section-230-csam-allegations-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Marvel%20Delays%20%E2%80%98Deadpool%203%2C%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%98Captain%20America%204%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Thunderbolts%E2%80%99%20in%20Post-Strike%20Disney%20Release%20Shake-Up%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699578240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2Fdeadpool-2-7.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235786760%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20months%20of%20speculation%20amid%20the%20wo