itionally%2C%20wealth%20offerings%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20create%20another%20%2430-40%20billion%20in%20revenue%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20the%20affluent%20segment%20in%20India%20corners%2070%25%20of%20retail%20deposits%20and%20conducts%2050-60%25%20of%20the%20overall%20online%20spends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20report%20comes%20at%20the%20same%20time%20when%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20announced%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20will%20be%20extending%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Garib%20Kalyan%20Anna%20Yojana%20(PM-GKAY)%20for%20the%20next%20five%20years.%20The%20scheme%20provides%20free%20ration%20to%2080%20crore%20poor%20people%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20experts%20have%20pointed%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20K-shaped%20recovery%2C%20which%20means%20that%20some%20parts%20of%20the%20economy%20are%20doing%20well%2C%20while%20others%20are%20struggling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%20for%20instance%2C%20after%20growing%20about%2025-40%25%20year-on-year%20in%20the%20second%20half%20of%202020%2C%20consumer%20goods%20firms%20are%20now%20finding%20it%20hard%20to%20remain%20in%20the%20black%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstoday.in%2Fmagazine%2Fdeep-dive%2Fstory%2Fbattered-by-inflation-and-faltering-demand-indias-consumer-goods-industry-is-ailing-399174-2023-09-21%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Frural-demand-slows-down-for-fmcg-11699029760068.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20rural%20demand%20saw%20a%20sluggish%20recovery%20in%20the%20September%20quarter.%20It%20said%20that%20while%20volumes%20have%20improved%20sequentially%20in%20the%20September%20quarter%2C%20companies%20said%20the%20pace%20of%20growth%20has%20been%20slow.%20It%20added%20that%20growth%20also%20came%20on%20a%20negative%20base%20of%20the%20previous%20year%20w