%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2Fapala-2-1669797157-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2Fapala-2-1669797157-150x78.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-304546%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22565%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIAS%20Apala%20Mishra%20secured%20the%20highest%20marks%20in%20the%20interview%20round.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Know%20your%20DAF%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EIAS%20officer%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F281857%2Fupsc-cse-interview-topper-ias-apala-mishra-score-personality-test%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApala%20Mishra%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20secured%20AIR%209%20in%20UPSC%20CSE%20and%20got%20the%20highest%20marks%20in%20the%20interview%20round%2C%20says%20that%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20things%20to%20remember%20for%20the%20personality%20round%20is%20the%20DAF%20(Detailed%20Application%20Form).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CEnsure%20that%20you%20put%20in%20only%20those%20attributes%20and%20strengths%20that%20you%20wish%20to%20highlight%20in%20the%20DAF.%20Do%20not%20put%20down%20any%20achievements%20or%20hobbies%20that%20you%20cannot%20explain.%20The%20interviewers%20are%20likely%20to%20see%20through%20it.%20Revise%20whatever%20you%20have%20mentioned%20and%20have%20answers%20to%20everything%20you%20put%20down.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20go%20unprepared%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Apala%20says%20that%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20myths%20is%20that%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20interview%20round%20as%20it%20will%20only%20test%20your%20personality.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20we%20need%20to%20understand%20that%20knowledge%2C%20too%2C%20forms%20the%20basis%20of%20our%20personality.%20It%20requires%20equal%20amounts%20of%20work%20that%20one%20puts%20in%20at%20the%20prelims%20and%20mains%20stage%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Focus%20on%20what%20you%20know%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F281037%2Fhow-to-crack-upsc-interview-tips-ias-officer-twitter-personality-test%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJitin%20Yadav%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%202016-batch%20IAS%20officer%2C%20says%20that%20having%20confidence%20in%20what%20you%20already%20know%20is%20more%20important%20than%20worrying%20about%20what%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDo%20not%20feel%20underconfident%20imagining%20how%20much%20you%20do%20not%20know.%20Focus%20on%20gaining%20confidence%20from%20how%20much%20you%20already%20know.%20If%20you%20are%20a%20serious%20aspirant%2C%20then%20that%20is%20more%20than%20enough%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E15%20Golden%20Tips%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FUPSC%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23UPSC%3C%2Fa%3E%20Civil%20Services%20Examination%20Personality%20Test%2FInterview%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%231%20Always%20allow%20the%20interview%20board%20member%20to%20interrupt%20you%20but%20never%20interrupt%20the%20board%20member.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%232%20Answer%20one%20question%20at%20a%20time.%20Never%20mix%20the%20previous%20question%20with%20the%20new%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Jitin%20Yadav%20(%40Jitin_IAS)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJitin_IAS%2Fstatus%2F1508890225270951937%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2029%2C%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5.%20Learn%20to%20be%20a%20good%20listener%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EJitin%20advises%20aspirants%20to%20be%20good%20listeners%20and%20take%20a%20pause%20before%20replying%20to%20a%20question.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20aspirants%20start%20framing%20their%20answers%20before%20the%20question%20is%20finished.%20Never%20do%20that%2C%20we%20end%20up%20giving%20incomplete%20answers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJitin%20points%20out%20that%20your%20ability%20to%20bounce%20back%20is%20tested%20in%20the%20personality%20test.%20%E2%80%9CToo%20many%20factual%20questions%20might%20be%20asked%2C%20and%20it%20is%20completely%20normal%20if%20not%20all%20can%20be%20answered%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E6.%20Be%20careful%20while%20responding%20to%20questions%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInterview%20is%20not%20a%20knowledge%20test%2C%20which%20has%20already%20been%20tested%20in%20the%20mains.%20Interview%20checks%20your%20personality%20traits%20via%20indirect%20methods%3B%20your%20response%20to%20questions%20will%20give%20them%20hints%20to%20assess%20your%20traits%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jitin.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E7.%20Keep%20your%20dress%20code%20simple%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20aspirants%20worry%20about%20what%20to%20wear%20during%20the%20personality%20test%2C%20IAS%20Jitin%20says%20that%20what%20you%20choose%20to%20wear%20does%20matter%20while%20appearing%20for%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20questions%20may%20come%20up%20regarding%20the%20brand%20or%20design.%20In%20my%20opinion%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20better%20to%20keep%20the%20outfit%20as%20simple%20as%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%237%20Optimum%20amount%20of%20nervousness%20is%20actually%20good%20for%20interview.%20If%20anxiety%20is%20in%20extremes%2C%20either%20too%20high%20or%20too%20low%2C%20then%20only%20it's%20a%20concern.%3Cbr%3E(Read%20Yerkes-Dodson%20Law%20%E2%8